  "texts": [
    "Smart contract technology has created a trustworthy environment for all Metaverse participants.",
    "It realizes the value transaction in the Metaverse and ensures that the system rules defined in contract codes are followed transparently.",
    "After being launched, the smart contract code cannot be altered.",
    "Every clause in these smart contracts must be fulfilled in full.",
    "Combining AI and blockchain is a trend that shows promise for promoting the development of the blockchain/AI-enabled Metaverse ecosystem."
  ]
}